Bile esculin agar (CC) -> Growth and esculin hydrolysis (BEcc)
Bile esculin agar (CC) -> No esculin hydrolysis (no blackening) (BEcc)
Growth and esculin hydrolysis (BEcc) -> Mannitol Salt Agar (MSA) (CC)
