Bacitracin sensitivity -> Sensitive to bacitracin
Bacitracin sensitivity -> Resistant to bacitracin
Resistant to bacitracin -> Group B/C Streptoccocus

Sensitive to bacitracin -> Streptococcus pyogenes: finalized species
Streptococcus pyogenes: {tooltip: confirm with Streptococcus grouping test}
Streptococcus pyogenes.shape: diamond

